description: GtpuSupervision: Table containing GTPU supervision data with timestamps, location, cell identifiers, and GTPU error indicators.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of record), Area_Name (geographic area of the cell), CellId (unique cell identifier), Id2 (duplicate of CellId?), Id3 (likely an identifier, needs further clarification), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (version of data format), GtpuErrorIndDscp (GTPU error indicator DSCP value), GtpuSupervision.gtpuSupervisionId (GTPU supervision ID).
queries: Show me all GtpuSupervision records from Area_Name 'Downtown' with GtpuErrorIndDscp > 100 in the last hour.
What is the distribution of `vsDataType` values for CellId 12345 across all `Area_Name`s?
Find all instances where `CellId` and `Id2` mismatch within the past day.
Generate a time series graph of `GtpuErrorIndDscp` for CellId 67890 in Area_Name 'Suburb A'.
Retrieve all distinct `Area_Name` values associated with `vsDataFormatVersion` 2.0 and `GtpuErrorIndDscp` equal to zero.
